beats

public boolean beats(PokerRank r)
Description copied from interface: Rank
Tests to see if this Rank trumps a given one, and returns accordingly. This relationship is not necessarily transitive, though it should be symmetric. In general, for a given Rank r, r.beats(r) == false.
